    <Container>
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Table of Contents</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          50 pages of actionable strategies, frameworks, and tools organized into easy-to-follow chapters.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <Card variant="elevated">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-primary">Part I: Foundation</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                <span class="text-primary font-bold text-sm">1</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold">CRO Fundamentals</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Understanding conversion psychology and user behavior</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                <span class="text-primary font-bold text-sm">2</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold">Analytics Setup</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Essential tracking and measurement configuration</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                <span class="text-primary font-bold text-sm">3</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold">Conversion Audit Framework</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Step-by-step website optimization assessment</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                <span class="text-primary font-bold text-sm">4</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold">User Research Methods</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Qualitative and quantitative research techniques</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </Card>

        <Card variant="elevated">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-accent-700">Part II: Implementation</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-accent-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                <span class="text-accent-700 font-bold text-sm">5</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold">A/B Testing Mastery</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Statistical significance, test design, and analysis</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-accent-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                <span class="text-accent-700 font-bold text-sm">6</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold">Landing Page Optimization</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">High-converting page elements and structure</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-accent-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                <span class="text-accent-700 font-bold text-sm">7</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold">Form & Checkout Optimization</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Reducing friction in conversion funnels</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-accent-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                <span class="text-accent-700 font-bold text-sm">8</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold">Mobile Conversion Strategies</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Mobile-specific optimization techniques</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </Card>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8">
        <Card variant="elevated">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-success">Part III: Advanced Strategies</h3>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-success-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                  <span class="text-success font-bold text-sm">9</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold">Personalization & Segmentation</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Dynamic content and targeted experiences</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-success-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                  <span class="text-success font-bold text-sm">10</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold">Psychology & Persuasion</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Cognitive biases and behavioral triggers</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-success-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                  <span class="text-success font-bold text-sm">11</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold">Advanced Testing Methods</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Multivariate, multi-page, and sequential testing</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-success-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                  <span class="text-success font-bold text-sm">12</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold">ROI Measurement & Reporting</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Proving and communicating CRO value</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-success-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                  <span class="text-success font-bold text-sm">13</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold">Building a CRO Program</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Team structure, processes, and scaling</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-success-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                  <span class="text-success font-bold text-sm">14</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold">Industry Case Studies</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Real-world examples and lessons learned</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </Card>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </Section>

  <!-- Testimonials -->
  <Section padding="lg">
    <Container>
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">What CRO Professionals Say</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Trusted by thousands of marketers, growth teams, and conversion specialists worldwide.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <Card variant="hover">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
              <span class="text-primary font-bold">JD</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">Jason Delacroix</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Growth Lead, TechStartup Inc.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            "This playbook saved us countless hours of trial and error. We implemented their audit framework and saw a 45% improvement in conversions within 8 weeks."
          </p>
          <div class="flex text-accent-600">
            ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐
          </div>
        </Card>

        <Card variant="hover">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-success-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
              <span class="text-success font-bold">MS</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">Maria Santos</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Marketing Director, E-commerce Co.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            "The A/B testing section alone is worth its weight in gold. Finally, a resource that explains statistical significance in plain English!"
          </p>
          <div class="flex text-accent-600">
            ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐
          </div>
        </Card>

        <Card variant="hover">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
