            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">Robert Kim</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">CRO Consultant, Freelance</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            "I've been doing CRO for 5 years and still learned new techniques from this guide. The psychology section is particularly insightful."
          </p>
          <div class="flex text-accent-600">
